Description: The wind turbine Aeolos-H 60kW is a production of Aeolos Wind Turbine, a manufacturer from United Kingdom. This manufacturer has been in business since 1986. The rated power of Aeolos Aeolos-H 60kW is 60,00 kW. At a wind speed of 3 m/s, the wind turbine starts its work. the cut-out wind speed is 25 m/s. The rotor diameter of the Aeolos Aeolos-H 60kW is 22,3 m. The rotor area amounts to 390,4 m². The wind turbine is equipped with 3 rotor blades. The Aeolos Aeolos-H 60kW is fittet with a direct drive gearbox. In the generator, Aeolos Wind Turbine sets to synchronous permanent. The manufacturer has used one generator for the Aeolos-H 60kW. At the mains frequency, the Aeolos-H 60kW is at 50 Hz. In the construction of the tower, the manufacturer uses steel tube. As corrosion protection for the tower Aeolos focuses on painted. We have 3 pictures of this wind turbine. There are no models for this wind turbine. Power data for the Aeolos-H 60kW of Aeolos are not stored in the system. The Aeolos Aeolos-H 60kW has been listed since 28.05.2018.
